short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Automatically redirects YouTube video pages to YouTube Music for a seamless music listening experience.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: The 'YouTube Music Redirector extension is the perfect tool for music enthusiasts who enjoy exploring and discovering content on YouTube. This extension adds an exclusive button to YouTube playback pages, allowing you to effortlessly open the same song or video in YouTube Music with just one click. Seamlessly transition your YouTube experience into a smoother music experience by enjoying your favorite content on the YouTube Music platform. Embrace a seamless transition from YouTube to YouTube Music and immerse yourself in an even more thrilling musical world.
